  "subject": "add SDC Client register logic support",
  "commit_message": "add SDC Client register logic support\n\n* Add PssdController to do initialize and close\n* Add PssdNotification to register a callback functional which to be\n  called once there is one notification from SDC/DMAAP automatically\n* Add Final/DistributionStatusMessage to compose a message to send\n  back to DMAAP/SDC\n* add unit test cases to mimic Distribution client behavior\n* integration into the SdcReceptionHandler so it could be controller from\n  the high level\n\nChange-Id: I69e3e98ef269e13beabea54e6129441cc8e65ae2\nIssue-ID: POLICY-974\nSigned-off-by: liboNet <libo.zhu@intel.com>\n",
